metadata.name: Happy Kitten Boys #1
metadata.description: This is how the story of the 10,000 happy kitten boys on the Ethereum blockchain begins, with Angel, Little Blue, and our endless love for them, thanks to which we have created a wonderful world where kittens from all over the world can live happily and who together with you will become stronger and will help as many kittens and other baby animals as possible in real life.
